  "tutorial": {
    "title": "Labs concoct spells",
    "body": "A Lab can brew one spell at a time. Hover your Lab and click Concoct \u2192 Freeze. After ~15 seconds it's ready.\n\nTo cast: drag from your ready Lab to any node. Freeze instantly neutralizes the target \u2014 its owner becomes neutral, units preserved.\n\nLabs can't produce units, only consume them. Keep yours topped up via friendly sends.\n\nThe red base is too strong to take by force. Freeze it, then capture the empty shell."
